+	<releases>
+		<release version="2.0" date="2022-12-16">
+			<description>
+				<p>
+					Version 2.0 commemorates the game's 10th anniversary by introducing many quality-of-life improvements.
+				</p>
+				<ul>
+					<li>Rewrote the game from the old <code>SDL 1.2</code> library to the newer <code>SDL 2.24</code> library.</li>
+					<li>Ported the game to Android.</li>
+					<li>Added a menu screen for customizing game zone colours.</li>
+					<li>
+						Improved performance of room scripts – instead of being parsed anew during each room change,
+						they are now parsed once during the loading phase and then executed from memory.
+					</li>
+				</ul>
+			</description>
+		</release>
+		<release version="1.3" date="2017-07-25">
+			<description>
+				<p>Version 1.3 brings various assorted fixes and improvements.</p>
+				<ul>
+					<li>Added support for navigating the menu using the mouse.</li>
+					<li>Made the green zone a little bit harder by adding an extra door that needs to be unlocked.</li>
+					<li>Fixed the hero getting stuck at edges of the screen instead of moving into next room.</li>
+					<li>Fixed some misaligned exits between rooms.</li>
+				</ul>
+			</description>
+		</release>
+		<release version="1.2" date="2014-03-16">
+			<description><p>
+				Version 1.2 replaces the proprietary <code>BASS</code> audio handling library with the free <code>SDL_mixer</code> library.
+			</p></description>
+		</release>
+		<release version="1.1" date="2012-12-26">
+			<description>
+				<p>Version 1.1 introduces multiple quality-of-life improvements.</p>
+				<ul>
+					<li>Added the save &amp; load feature. The game will be saved automatically upon progress, or death.</li>
+					<li>Added a tutorial world.</li>
+					<li>Added a menu screen for changing the key bindings.</li>
+					<li>Added possibility to change game window size.</li>
+					<li>Added audio volume control.</li>
+					<li>Added the &quot;pause&quot; feature.</li>
+					<li>Fixed minor issues with enemy AI.</li>
+				</ul>
+			</description>
+		</release>
+		<release version="1.0" date="2012-12-17">
+			<description><p>
+				Initial release.
+			</p></description>
+		</release>
+	</releases>
